n offer. Xxx makes every effort to ensure that the content of this website is kept up-to-date, complete and correct. Since this information can, however, be subject to rapid changes it is impossible to guarantee that it is absolutely up-to-date, correct and complete.&nbsp;The information given on this website does not represent any binding aid to making a decision or answers to issues requiring advice, nor should any labour law-related or other decisions be made based on this information. Any and all activities resulting from the information published on this website take place at the sole risk of the user.\r\n\r\n<h2>This website&rsquo;s functions</h2>\r\n{CONTACT_COMPANY} accepts no responsibility and gives no warranty for the long-term, uninterrupted availability of the functions provided on this website or for their being free of errors or that the website or the corresponding server are free of viruses or any other damaging components.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>No secure data transmission</h2>\r\nE-mail communication takes place via an open, publically accessible, cross-border network. It cannot thus be ruled out that the transmitted data may be accessed by third parties and the establishment of the contact thus also traced.\r\n\r\n<h2>Data protection</h2>\r\n{CONTACT_COMPANY} reserves the right to gather and evaluate personal data transmitted to it electronically for its own marketing purposes. In this context the provisions of the Swiss Federal Data Protection Act will be complied with and the data will not be forwarded to third parties.<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Exclusion of liability</h2>\r\nThis website&rsquo;s content includes no promises or warranties whatsoever. {CONTACT_COMPANY}&nbsp;accepts no liability whatsoever, including negligence and third party liability, for any direct, indirect or consequential damages arising from use of the information and material published on this website or from access to other websites via the links provided on this